data.title: Inside Burundi's former capital: Bujumbura – DW – 08
data.meta_description: Located on the shores of Lake Tanganyika, Burundi's largest city is warm and welcoming with plenty of spots to kick back and relax. Local singer Monna Walda Kaneza — AKA Mo'W Kanzie — shows you the highlights of her hometown.
data.text:
08/12/2022August 12, 2022

Located on the shores of Lake Tanganyika, Burundi's largest city is warm and welcoming with plenty of spots to kick back and relax. Local singer Monna Walda Kaneza — AKA Mo'W Kanzie — shows you the highlights of her hometown.
